item.title: Getting Started with LESS
item.dc:creator: Swayam Patwa
item.description: Less is a CSS pre-processor, meaning that it extends the CSS language, adding features that allow variables, mixins, functions and many other techniques that allow you to make CSS that is more maintainable, themable and extendable.
